data.title: James Stroud Classical Guitar Competition Final Round
data.meta_description: The fifth annual James Stroud Classical Guitar Competition will feature outstanding classical guitar students ages 14-18 from around the US competing for cash prizes.
data.text:
The fifth annual James Stroud Classical Guitar Competition will feature outstanding classical guitar students ages 14-18 from around the US competing for cash prizes.

For the full schedule and more information, visit guitarsint.com/stroud_competition

Ticket Information

Admission is free and open to the public.
